summary: A small stealthy based player home with several new items for a stealth based bowman/woman/other. The home is located West of Falkreath.
descriptionHtml:
Details and Lore:
A small stealthy based player home with several new items for a stealth based bowman/woman/other. The home is based off of a Whiterun guard named Caitlyn who left a set of spare armor there. Though she commonly goes there to get away from it all. She has seemingly forgot about it and left it to whomever finds it next. The reasons why are in the filled up journal on the end table on the balcony

Hint:The home is located West of Falkreath. 

Manual Installation:
1.) Download zip file from Skyrim Nexus manually.
2.) Unzip file into documents (Or any makeshift folder)
3.) Copy or Move ESP file to the Data folder in Skyrim steam folder,

v1.1 update and bug fixes
Yes day one and I\'ve had bug fixes.
1. Allows for a way to get down without falling damage
2. Provides back story on Caitlyn Carringswood A Whiterun Guard and the reason the armor is there
3. Got rid of the damned wolf
4. Fixed floating trees
5. Added Arrows
6. Spruced up the environment with banners and making the scaffold look more appealing by making it structurally sound
7. Added a tanning rack
More to come (:

About this mod:
Keep in mind this is my first mod... Ever. I would love feedback and suggestions are very much so open. I plan on doing more in the future with the more I learn from friends, videos and even strangers. Do report anything to me and please, Feedback, I\'d love it. Can\'t thank enough people but I hope you enjoy! -Chanson93
